column16: Jason Kendall pops out to second baseman Gordon Beckham in foul territory.
Scott Podsednik grounds out, pitcher Jeffrey Marquez to first baseman Paul Konerko.
Yuniesky Betancourt homers (6) on a fly ball to left field.   Mitch Maier scores.
Mitch Maier singles on a line drive to right fielder Andruw Jones.
Willie Bloomquist grounds out, shortstop Alexei Ramirez to first baseman Paul Konerko.
